{"tid":371944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★環保等於焗死 政府行人天橋升降機無抽風+經常故障","createTime":"2017-08-24T04:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T12:17:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a284544c62f80c21b8170a2d01be1e6bba694ce","tid":371944,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"【記者朱先儒、陳素貞報道】環保等於焗死？路政署推出「人人暢道通行計劃」，為部分行人天橋加裝升降機接駁以便利居民及殘障人士出入，升降機聲稱要節能減碳，故只裝機械環保通風系統，冷氣機欠奉，惟本報發現有升降機的抽風系統在攝氏三十三度高溫下仍沒有啟動，巿民被迫「焗到一身濕晒」，更有升降機啟用兩周即經常故障，市民仍要行上行落，有油尖旺區議員接獲十多宗居民投訴，要求當局解釋及改善。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者本月十五日到橫跨櫻桃街、渡船街及塘尾道的行人天橋，視察剛於上月底啟用的兩部升降機，升降機內貼有告示指「升降機採用機械式環保通風系統，不設冷氣機」，但抽風系統無開啟。記者用溫度計量度其中一部升降機內溫度，錄得介乎攝氏三十三點二度至三十三點五，較升降機外的三十二度還要高出一點五度。油尖旺區議員余德寶指「一人搭（升降機）就問題不大，六、七人逼埋一齊就好焗，而升降機顯示可乘載十二人。」記者曾到荃灣、黃大仙區等有安裝接駁天橋的升降機量度溫度，發現無安裝冷氣的升降機內的溫度普遍在攝氏三十度以上，非常悶焗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">倘困升降機有機會焗暈</span><br />\n<br />\n余指接駁亞皆老街行人天橋的升降機上月底才啟用，但啟用兩周即常故障，已有十四、五名巿民向他投訴。由於該升降機主要接駁往旺角街巿及港鐵站，使用率極高，他擔心升降機常故障，加上通風不足，巿民被困升降機時有機會焗暈，已去信區議會反映，求政府部門及承辦商處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170824/photo/0824-00176-053b3.jpg?t=1503547621796\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170824%2Fphoto%2F0824-00176-053b3.jpg%3Ft%3D1503547621796&h=03462d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170824/00176_053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170824%2F00176_053.html&d=uoHoe%2BvgZMG8dYuN5Ef8pp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7914f0b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170824/00176_053.html</a>"},{"pid":"074e087fcc84b72afeb2add44307802418f1c403","tid":371944,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426d4845b8130d40038c6802042761d692cb1b81","tid":371944,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港燦：怕焗可以唔搭</span></span>"},{"pid":"244e1d5edf6287bed5eeec18b2d363fafe76f156","tid":371944,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"焗爐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254e8c9b52dbce50ac1f1857f98f07da94da4b73","tid":371944,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"慳電就慳電啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cc62fc953bc8cfa4ee42a4e7d4c465afe70dcd","tid":371944,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:27:19.000Z","msg":"通風系統唔定期清理積塵，仲會熱上加熱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dd729ee5bffe5ceb0ab425ed26a68d90e5a1e7","tid":371944,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次就唔派膠，屌得好<br />\n<br />\n不過一樣呼喚蓋清嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673b13dc666c24516e5340bae35e5fc3fb325f4c","tid":371944,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5965bf8786762b8233de1626dd1a37c7f57dacd8","tid":371944,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/fa